title: Find Your Way Around the FME Academy

questions.question: What’s a course?
options: A guided learning path through several learning topics
A project for you to work on and submit to Safe Software for official grading
A single learning topic that rewards you with a badge on completion
A single learning subtopic on one page

questions.question: How do you advance ranks?
options: By seniority: The longer you’ve had an FME Academy account, the higher your rank is.
You earn points and badges by completing courses.
You submit a data integration project to Safe Software for official grading.
